<P>
How refreshing to have so much discourse on drugs and legalization (Drugs: 
America Looks for the Way Out, Op-Ed Page, March 12-21). Now, maybe we can try 
something new instead of staying with laws that haven't worked. 
</P>
<P>
Regarding the numerous authors: Carol Tavris ("Drop the Iron Fist and Try Rules 
