<P>
Unocal to Sell Norwegian Unit: Unocal Corp. said it would sell its Norwegian 
oil and gas subsidiary to a unit of Paris-based Total CFP, a French oil 
company, for $322 million. The sale of Unocal Norge A/S to Total Marine Norsk 
A/S includes Unocal's 18% interest in the Veslefrikk oil field in the North 
Sea, Unocal spokesman Michael Thacher said in Los Angeles. The sale, which is 
subject to Norwegian government approval, is expected to close in May. 
