ATLANTIC CITY (NJ); CASINOS; HOTELS; FIRST EXECUTIVE CORP; SABRE ASSOCIATES; 
GOLDSMITH, JAY; FREUND, HARRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
