</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032690-0075 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 195274 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 26, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 5; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
230 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
MARKET WATCH; 
</P>
<P>
WEEKLY SCORECARD; 
</P>
<P>
STOCK GROUP WINNERS &amp; LOSERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Best- and worst-performing industries and companies in each group, with closing 
stock price, for the week ended March 23. Only stocks trading for $1 or higher 
are included. 
</P>
<P>
